Title: Series: Palazzo Granducale in Firenze
Description: Rest on the flight into Egypt: landscape with in the centre foreground the holy Family resting under a clump of trees; some angels are picking fruits and handing them to St Joseph; on the right, a woman puts her hand on a large basket; after a painting attributed by the inscription to Palma Vecchio; before letter Etching
Curator's comments: For comment on series see 1861,0608.278. The painting is not described in Rylands, 'Palma Vecchio, l'opera completa', 1988.
Acquisition name: Purchased from: A E Evans & Sons
